choices.text:
just next door - there is a market with all the goods you might need. Sometimes carts are doing the same, but generally it is just nice talking with the people working there, and sometimes you just need a splash of hand soap. There is also the bigger stores Wyndemere, Mega and Soriana just a 5-10minute drive away where you find the goods you would belooking for in your home country.

Our house is great for intimate small family holidays (starting vacation with just the two of us is great!) and excellent for Meetings, creative projects, film projects, team building and retreats in. We cater for up to 8 people by invitation.

You can reach us by phone (Mexico & US) & email (Germany) .. Comfortable & average standard accommodation in heart of the city. 2 queen size beds in each bedroom. Living room & terrace furniture's under roof on upper floors.

Finally: These prices are for 2 adults in the entire house, each added person is 100 Pesos/day & 1 kid under 5 years is free.

Excursions:

You can reach many interesting places to visit within one hour in car, like colonial Taxco, Boulderstrewn Teotihuacan, Mining Tiles town Taxco or the Nature Paradise San Isidro. Alternatively you can simply take a day trip to the jungle and beach of Cuatlapanga.
